				<div itemprop="commentText" class='post entry-content '>
					Thanks for the example, kicken. There are a few things that aren&#39;t obvious to me from your example.<br />
<br />
1. What is an &quot;E_NOTICE&quot;? You refer to them after the example but I don&#39;t see any variables with that name so I&#39;m not sure what you mean.<br />
2. What is the significance of the .tpl file extension on the last file? I&#39;ve never seen that one before. I&#39;m guessing it is short for &quot;template&quot; but I&#39;m not sure what the effect is of executing code with a .tpl extension is in a PHP environment.<br />
3. Is this approach safe from injection attacks? How would it have to change to be safe?
					
